In [55]:
df_list = []
for i in range(1, len(dong.columns)-1):
    globals()['m' + str(i) + str(i+1)] = dong[['행정구역', dong.columns[i]]]
    globals()['m' + str(i) + str(i+1)] = pd.concat([globals()['m' + str(i) + str(i+1)], dong[[dong.columns[i+1]]]], axis =1)
    df_list.append(globals()['m' + str(i) + str(i+1)])
